    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is in absolute mint condition, appearing exactly as it did when it first rolled off the showroom floor. The exterior paint is flawless, with zero chips, scratches, or imperfections, and the interior still retains that new-car smell with no signs of wear on the upholstery. Mechanically, it is perfect, having been meticulously maintained with a full service history. Buyers can expect a car that needs absolutely nothing and represents the pinnacle of its model's condition.",
      "price": 48500.0,
      "reputation": 1.0,
